== Spanish ==
=== Etymology ===
Latin ''[[trans]]''
=== Preposition ===
'''tras'''
# After
# Beyond
=== Usage note===
''Tras'' may be found in written language, but in speech, it is usually replaced with ''[[atrás]] [[de#Spanish|de]]'', ''[[detrás]] de'' or ''[[después]] de''.

